"config_property_copy_button:+++quarkus.management.host-validation.allowed-hosts+++[]\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"[.description]\n"
"--\n"
"Allowed hosts.\n"
"\n"
"A comma-separated set of hosts, for example: \"localhost\", \"quarkus.io\".\n"
"\n"
"Note this property is mutually exclusive with the `require-localhost()` property.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Environment variable: env_var_with_copy_button:+++QUARKUS_MANAGEMENT_HOST_VALIDATION_ALLOWED_HOSTS+++[]\n"
"--"
